Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that. That big schedule\Nboard got torn apart by a wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the power of this ebbing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The speed of the waves of\Nthis Aqua Laguna are abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?! So Sanji went\Nto the station after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, anyway, no matter what means\Nwe take to follow the sea train,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't do anything unless\Nwe find Luffy and Zoro first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:01:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry... Aurora Flicker... Jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brochette!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Pirate lady! Hey, look over there!\NThere's something there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? That straw hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your King of the Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go down to the backstreets!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna lose your life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is already coming! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy! The pirate\Nwoman went down the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come back! Don't go down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--Don't go to the backstreets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like all of you going\Nis enough to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sea we're up against!\NYou'll just end up sharing her fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens,\NI will handle things myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys just stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She jumped off to the backstreets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, she makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, she's headed for Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right! Now let's move forward{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with the sun always in our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As power passes through our clasped hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}let's grab hold of our wishes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Working together, let's ride the giant waves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be a journey fraught with injury{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but what you cherish most will be right there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if you get into a jam{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always be there to protect you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right! Now let's move forward{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with the sun always in our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and gaze at the light beyond{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we gather up the pieces of our dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they'll make a map leading to tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So let's grab hold of our wishes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}under the same flag-- together, we're one{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One Piece{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:16.00,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Nami's Soul Cries Out!\NStraw Hat Luffy Makes a Comeback!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unbelievable that she\Ncan run someplace like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots! This is no time to be impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come back right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be swallowed by the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea anemone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea anemone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea anemone is coming out\Nof a chimney. Why a sea anemone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea anemone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...! Hey, wait, reindeer! Not you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin made a deal with\NCP9 by giving up everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for a wish that couldn't come\Ntrue if she was with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the six Straw Hats, excluding me,\Ncan leave this island safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, I don't care if the weapon is\Nbrought back or the world is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Wait! We'll fight for you\Nno matter who we're up against!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:07:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate lady! You're so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't make it back in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look offshore! The wave\Nis almost here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot! They're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't make it back anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Zoro! Can you hear me?! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it. I can't go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N... Nami! Are you there behind me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hey, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, that pigeon guy sent me flying
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I flew right into this gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fool around at a critical time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you've been taking your\Nsweet time, Robin was taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin intends to die for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sacrificed herself in order to protect\Nus from an attack by the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place for me to go or go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are. I'll never see you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she knew that she was going\Nto be killed if she was taken in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...after all, Robin was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let Robin die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that? It really is\Nseveral times bigger than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This is seriously bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate woman! Give up and run already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! I'm being torn apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't coming out!\NHow'd you get in there, Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owwww! Don't pull me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do?!\NThe huge wave is almost here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What're we gonna do"? How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Wait a sec. Are you carrying\Nthe Kitetsu by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? One of your swords?\NYes, I am. How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For just that one, I can tell,\Nsince it's a cursed sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were carrying it\Nfor me, Chopper? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hold it in my hand! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Climb up to a high place! Go to a higher place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, this is it! They're not gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be swallowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is already so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:14:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! What the hell?! He broke the buildings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Sword Style! Thirty-six Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! What the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble! Jumping Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on to me, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... The backstreets are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:15:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that! It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be safe, since they\Ngot to the Great Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As big as the wave may be, it can't reach there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good going, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! It's come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the Straw Hats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they get swallowed by Aqua Laguna?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not safe yet! Run!\NRun to the shipbuilding island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Bridge is gonna collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wave...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Unbelievable...\NThis is the shipbuilding island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even staying here doesn't seem safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The tide is ebbing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just natural. It'll keep coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second wave... The third wave...\NJust like the one we just saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us evacuate to a higher place, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... That was reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. You saved us, rope guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked! So that's Aqua Laguna...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't stop shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a big one like that had hit us every year,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this island would be long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's Aqua Laguna is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are really crazy.\NI'm surprised you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Monster Granny.\NSo you were on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! If we stayed in the middle\Nof the sea like that, we'd drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Pirate guy!\NYou were incredible! Like, wham!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to suffocate me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This idiot lost consciousness\Nwhile holding on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...? Come to think of it, Zoro,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why were you also being chased by the wave?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you in the lower side of town?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? W-Well, not particularly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was stuck in a chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuck in a chimney?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so clumsy, Zoro!\NWhat'd you have to do to be in that situ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in any position to be laughing\Nat others?! You both are super clumsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Then what happened to\NSanji and Uso... I mean, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... There're lots of things I need\Nto tell you. You listen, too, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my big chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Buster Call, we can urgently summon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,five of the Navy Headquarters'\Nvice admirals as well as ten battleships.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is thanks to Aokiji for giving us,\NCP9, the authority to exercise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think, Funkfreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin, the woman whom the World\NGovernment has been pursuing for 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has fallen straight into the hands of us, CP9.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, along with her,\Nwe're taking in that detestable Cutty Flam,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that disciple of Tom's who\Nhas the blueprints for Pluton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only two people hold the key to\Nthe ancient weapon in this vast world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And these two are on the sea train\Nheaded to me right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The military force strong enough to\Ndestroy the world is headed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your prince on a white horse is coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that Nico Robin\Nsacrificed herself for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the cook and Usopp are on the same train?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wanna do, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sail out right away and follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're off... to rescue Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.61,0:22:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We had a dream that day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our belief in ourselves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're braver and more caring than anyone else{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.72,0:22:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you ever depart this ship\Nand live in a different world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:23:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, we can all surely smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let us borrow a ship!\NA strong and fast one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.92,0:23:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. You can't make it through this storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.05,0:23:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you leave now,\Nthere's no chance you'd survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter!\NOur friends are waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one way-- just one way--\Nto get through this Aqua Laguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Another Sea Train? Rocketman Charges Forth!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
